						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in front of the Siddhēśvara temple in the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1165, Śōbhakṛit, Phālguṇa, ba. 8, Thursday.</p>						

						<p>Records the gift of land to the temple of Siddhanāthadēva at Tēṟāla by Pōtinēni Tripiri Nāyuḍu.</p>						

